
  
  .hero-section {
   
    height: calc(100% - 80px); //change korchi akhane
    
    }
    
     nav {
        height:80px
     }
     
     header er total height chilo 100vh..nav er jonno height deya hyc 80px.akhn hero section er jonno height dite hobe...jehutu headerer total height
     100vh tai total height theke nav er height ta minus kore hero-section k dite hobe..exmaple : 100vh - 80px..but avabe na likhe .hero-section k likhe dichi
     calc(100% - 80px).mane parent element k vh diye height bole dite porer child element % diye prokas kora jay..
